positive.review:
The hydric engineering + changing climatic conditions are fun and challenging. The world building is pretty and rich. Man see menbeavers accomplishing feats of engineering, having children and living happily, man happy!

What I miss:

- rain and more immersive/realistic weather;
- better quality of life, I miss things like templates and undo;
- load bearing and water load mechanics but that is asking too much.
